<paragraph id="964A0933C101FFE826A6F34079A9F98E" blockId="1.[151,1437,1080,1599]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">
Notes. 
<bibRefCitation id="F26474C2C101FFE82775F3407891FAF5" author="Fu, C. M. &amp; Owada, M. &amp; Wu, S. &amp; Ronkay, L." box="[276,448,1323,1348]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592" pagination="333 - 349" refId="ref3312" refString="Fu, C. M., Owada, M., Wu, S. &amp; Ronkay, L. (2021) Erebidae, Hypeninae. In: Fu, C. - M., Owada, M., Shih, L. C. &amp; Lin, H. - H. (Eds.), Moths of Nanheng. Part 2. Endemic Species Research Institute, Nantou. pp. 333 - 349." type="book chapter" year="2021">
Fu 
<emphasis id="A481D521C101FFE82758F340783BFAF2" box="[313,362,1323,1347]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">et al</emphasis>
. (2021)
</bibRefCitation>
pointed out the imperfect revision of 
<taxonomicName id="51F572B0C101FFE8253EF3477AE1FAF2" authorityName=", Toth &amp; Ronkay" authorityYear="2014" box="[863,944,1323,1347]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Naarda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="592" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A481D521C101FFE8253EF3477AE1FAF2" box="[863,944,1323,1347]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">Naarda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by Tóth &amp; Ronkay as follows: “This species [
<taxonomicName id="51F572B0C101FFE826C1F33C7864FAD6" authorityName=": Toth &amp; Ronkay" authorityYear="2014" box="[160,309,1360,1383]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Naarda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="592" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctirena">
<emphasis id="A481D521C101FFE826C1F33C7864FAD6" box="[160,309,1360,1383]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="592">N. punctirena</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
] was described by 
<bibRefCitation id="F26474C2C101FFE8246DF3237BDCFAD9" author="Sugi, S." box="[524,653,1359,1384]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592" pagination="355 - 380" refId="ref3463" refString="Sugi, S. (1982) Noctuidae (excluding Herminiinae). In: Inoue, H., Sugi, S., Kuroko, H., Moriuti, S., Kawabe, A. &amp; Owada, M. (Eds.), Moths of Japan. Vols. 1 - 2. Kodansha, Tokyo, pp. 669 - 913 &amp; pp. 334 - 405, pls. 37 + 164 - 223 + 229 + 278 + 355 - 380." type="journal article" year="1982">Sugi (1982)</bibRefCitation>
from Ishigakijima and Iriomotejima Islands, the Yaeyama group of the Ryukyus. 
<bibRefCitation id="F26474C2C101FFE82763F31F7B53FA3D" author="Toth, B. &amp; Ronkay, L." box="[258,514,1395,1420]" pageId="1" pageNumber="592" pagination="1 - 49" refId="ref3670" refString="Toth, B. &amp; Ronkay, L. (2014 a) Revision of the Palaearctic and Oriental species of the genus Naarda Walker, 1866 (Lepidoptera: Erebidae, Hypeninae). Part 1. Taxonomic notes and description of 28 new species from Asia. Oriental Insects, 48 (1 - 2), 1 - 49. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00305316.2014.959790" type="journal article" year="2014">Tóth &amp; Ronkay (2014a)</bibRefCitation>
